{"type": "article", "id": 14779, "title": "皮质与木头的家具组件", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-11T07:11:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000328KIvaw6RWVZ8yXpDb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自丹麦设计工作室 by Wirth 的家具组件，都是用皮带和橡木做的。如装饰的架子使用橡木固定，皮带连接了放置物品的木板和固定的木桩，使这件家具有一个软硬之间的协调，比全木框的架子多了生动的感受，很有人情味。同样的效果也产生在皮带和玻璃杯之间，可以用皮带将他们栓在墙上，也增加了一份手感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142228TIcLA9lM87Y2hNV6.jpg\" width=\"993\" height=\"1280\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.28902316\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142228hc8EUXTNYaGmLq06.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142230GqKtkwnbLIC7alu8.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"900\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}